sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant UI as React Dashboard
  participant Backend as Node.js Backend
  participant Broker as MQTT Broker
  participant Node as ESP32 Node

  User->>UI: Send override command
  UI->>Backend: POST command
  Backend->>Broker: Publish MQTT command
  Broker->>Node: Deliver command
  Node->>Node: Apply override
  Node->>Broker: Publish acknowledgment/state
  Broker->>Backend: Forward acknowledgment
  Backend->>UI: Push updated state
